<br>
That book got me thinking..What if we move through life thinking that would could do just about anything and science would be there to get us out of a jam..<br>
<br>
What if science couldn't come through for us...<br>
<br>
Some of you have to keep in mind that science may be able to solve almost any problem, but can they solve it in time.....<br>
